object.script: function onTick() fluids = {} resource_0_type = input.getNumber(1) resource_1_type = input.getNumber(2) resource_2_type = input.getNumber(3) fluids[resource_0_type] = fluids[resource_0_type] or 0 + input.getNumber(4) fluids[resource_1_type] = fluids[resource_1_type] or 0 + input.getNumber(5) fluids[resource_2_type] = fluids[resource_2_type] or 0 + input.getNumber(6) output.setNumber(2, fluids[2] or 0) output.setNumber(1, fluids[1] or 0) output.setNumber(5, fluids[5] or 0) end
